description: Hot dog carts are the ancestors of the food trucks that we know and love today. After all this time, these carts have remained in the reverent hearts of American foodies, and it’s no wonder that Looy’s Dogs, LLC. is rockin’ it with their high-quality hot dogs and countless condiments. Whether it’s a whooshing Wisconsin winter or mild Midwestern summer... hot diggity dog, Looy’s will be there and their delicious dogs will sure hit the spot.
name: Looy's Dogs
